underlying_goal: The user wanted to commit all current changes in the working directory into logical, well-structured commits.
primary_success: Claude successfully analyzed a set of disparate changes and organized them into four logical, well-messaged commits, cleaning the working tree.
brief_summary: The user asked Claude to commit the current work. Claude analyzed the git status and diffs, organized the changes into four logical commits (documentation, feature configuration, deployment infrastructure, and new session data), and successfully committed them. The working tree was left clean.
